About Us

Our small family-owned eatery, Uncle Sammy, started as a cozy neighborhood spot in 1974. What began as a passion project has flourished into a local favorite, thanks to our dedication to fresh ingredients and time-honored recipes.

Specialties include artisan pizzas baked in our wood-fired oven, house-made pastas, and daily chef’s specials that highlight seasonal produce. Whenever possible, we source ingredients locally—supporting nearby farmers and ensuring the freshest flavors.

Whether you’re celebrating a special occasion or simply looking for a cozy dinner, our doors are always open. We look forward to serving you with warmth, hospitality, and great food.
